The '''Koboth Insurgent Mantle''' was an award given to [[Kobok/Legends|Koboks]] who earned distinction in a series of skirmishes during the [[Mavvan Conflict]].

[[Gaff]] the Kobok wore a Koboth Insurgent Mantle.

